{"tid":2215531,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"區議員黃學禮否認阻差 反對警員匿名及屏風後作供","createTime":"2020-09-24T05:09:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T05:22:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"66c5a304630a2420bba332cb7c5f4d8b3bf7ec66","tid":2215531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:09:37.000Z","msg":"市民去年包圍深水埗警署示威，聲援在深水埗購買觀星筆後被捕的浸大學生會會長方仲賢，警方多次施放催淚彈驅散人群。示威期間沙田區議員黃學禮到場了解，被警察制服並以涉嫌襲警拘捕，事後被控阻差辦公。黃學禮今在西九龍法院否認控罪，控方申請報稱受阻的警員匿名、使用屏風作供及用特別通道出入法庭，辯方反對，雙方押後爭辯。<br />\n<br />\n控方申請審訊時將警務人員A身份保密，安排其使用特別通道及屏風，並指已得悉辯方將會提出爭議。案件押後至11月23日作審前覆核，控辯雙方須在當日之前，向法庭呈交爭論警員匿命令及使用屏風的書面理據大綱。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/A7FFYNKTABFRNILJDJE5QCKXLQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FA7FFYNKTABFRNILJDJE5QCKXLQ%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=67d6c81b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200924%2FA7FFYNKTABFRNILJDJE5QCKXLQ%2F&h=2f4d69bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200924/A7FFYNKTABFRNILJDJE5QCKXLQ/</a>"},{"pid":"b8a2e74b348ffbc4f80184db089e716bcd44fe17","tid":2215531,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ded9ce549d587951e4816d82959d815c4ee0798","tid":2215531,"uid":132265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T05:13:35.000Z","msg":"不是性侵受害者先用嘅咩？"},{"pid":"081f5f42c25f19fb9b5e2b61d878